  "body": "#### System information\r\n\r\nErigon version: `erigon version 2022.99.99-dev-25ab6455`\r\n\r\nOS & Version: Linux using default docker-compose.yml\r\n\r\n#### Expected behaviour\r\nReturns TransactionReceipt JSON\r\n\r\n#### Actual behaviour\r\nCall to eth_getTransactionReceipt errors with:\r\n```\r\ncurl -X POST -s --data '{\"jsonrpc\":\"2.0\",\"method\":\"eth_getTransactionReceipt\",\"params\":[\"0xcc2588e34ed1111cf1553c0b0884c4069c0173b2073af76bc29196707dee7bbc\"],\"id\":1}' http://localhost:8545/ -H \"Content-Type: application/json\" | jq . \r\n{\r\n  \"jsonrpc\": \"2.0\",\r\n  \"id\": 1,\r\n  \"error\": {\r\n    \"code\": -32000,\r\n    \"message\": \"method handler crashed\"\r\n  }\r\n}\r\n```\r\nrpc logs say:\r\n```\r\nrpcdaemon_1   | [EROR] [04-24|23:31:18.121] RPC method eth_getTransactionReceipt crashed: runtime error: index out of range [0] with length 0\r\nrpcdaemon_1   | [service.go:217 panic.go:1038 panic.go:90 block_reader.go:569 block_reader.go:602 block_snapshots.go:312 block_reader.go:601 eth_backend.go:186 eth_api.go:136 eth_receipts.go:271 value.go:556 value.go:339 service.go:222 handler.go:484 handler.go:389 handler.go:343 handler.go:181 handler.go:271 asm_amd64.s:1581] \r\nrpcdaemon_1   | [WARN] [04-24|23:31:18.121] Served                                   conn=172.27.0.1:56976 method=eth_getTransactionReceipt reqid=1 t=292.978Âµs err=\"method handler crashed\"\r\n```\r\nMost calls to `eth_getTransactionReceipt` work fine but about 1% error with this error.\r\n\r\n#### Steps to reproduce the behavior\r\n`curl -X POST -v -s --data '{\"jsonrpc\":\"2.0\",\"method\":\"eth_getTransactionReceipt\",\"params\":[\"0xcc2588e34ed1111cf1553c0b0884c4069c0173b2073af76bc29196707dee7bbc\"],\"id\":1}' http://localhost:8545/ -H \"Content-Type: application/json\"`\r\n\r\n",
